ities. In the adult sentinel system, cases were reported from a sample of approximately 450 inpatient hospitals. In April 2006, the adult definition was changed from age >18 years to age >15 years. However, some pediatric facilities continued to report persons aged >15 years.\n† April–December only.\n§ Per 100,000 population.\n¶ Measles-containing vaccine, 1 dose.\n** The second dose of measles-containing vaccine was added in 2006","hasAlt":true,"isDecorative":false,"isMissingAlt":false,"ariaHidden":false,"rolePresentation":false,"renderedWidth":641,"renderedHeight":402,"naturalWidth":641,"naturalHeight":402,"loading":null,"decoding":null,"altVerdict":"TOO_LONG","altReason":"alt text is 1817 characters — consider a caption or description","bytes":62860},{"src":"https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/images/spacer.gif","alt":" ","hasAlt":true,"isDecorative":false,"isMissingAlt":false,"ariaHidden":false,"rolePresentation":false,"renderedWidth":10,"renderedHeight":1,"naturalWidth":10,"naturalHeight":10,"loading":null,"decoding":null,"altVerdict":"DECORATIVE","altReason":"alt=\"\" (decorative)","bytes":821},{"src":"https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/headers_footers/images/spacer1.gif","alt":"","hasAlt":true,"isDecorative":true,"isMissingAlt":false,"ariaHidden":false,"rolePresentation":false,"renderedWidth":1,"renderedHeight":1,"naturalWidth":10,"naturalHeight":10,"loading":null,"decoding":null,"altVerdict":"DECORATIVE","altReason":"alt=\"\" (decorative)","bytes":821},{"src":"https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/images/spacer1.gif","alt":"","hasAlt":true,"isDecorative":true,"isMissingAlt":false,"ariaHidden":false,"rolePresentation":false,"renderedWidth":1,"renderedHeight":1,"naturalWidth":10,"naturalHeight":10,"loading":null,"decoding":null,"altVerdict":"DECORATIVE","altReason":"alt=\"\" (decorative)","bytes":821},{"src":"https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/images/s.gif","alt":"","hasAlt":true,"isDecorative":true,"isMissingAlt":false,"ariaHidden":false,"rolePresentation":false,"renderedWidth":20,"renderedHeight":1,"n